      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for your absolute dream ride? This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot, with a spotless interior and a shine that'll turn heads everywhere you go. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with how smooth it is!",
