    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a standout example of the 997.2 generation. This specimen features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering a linear 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with zero signs of bore scoring or rear main seal weeping. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory limited-slip differential, the chassis remains taut with crisp turn-in and exceptional damping. The exterior finish retains its original factory depth, while the cabin remains free of bolster wear or switchgear delamination. This is a turn-key, investment-quality driver with a fully documented service pedigree.",
      "price": 48500.0,
