      "description": "For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality specimen. Every inch of the original factory paint has been preserved under a high-end ceramic coating, reflecting a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory matte finish with no bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent still lingers. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. From the pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber to the spotless engine bay, this is a turn-key investment for a buyer who values excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
