      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. I have babied this car since the day I got it, and it's still in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, smoke-free, and meticulously detailed. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for this beauty to go to a great new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
